\par\b\fs28 6. Local Setup (Developer)\b0\fs22\par
\par 1. Install PHP 8+ and MySQL.
\par 2. Place repo under web root (e.g., `htdocs/Asimos` for XAMPP).
\par 3. Import DB schema/data.
\par 4. Configure DB credentials.
\par 5. Open `/Asimos/index.php` and test each role login.
